
## Directory Structure rules.
- You should make seperate directory with git repositories for all of your outputs from yml files.
- You should make .gitignore files refer to gitignore.io with yml requirements.

## Database Rules.
- Do not directly connect with database.
- You can use ORM first when using spring boot or nest.js 
- Please re-ask to user which frameworks are preffered
- When you re-ask this, you must offer major options.

## Self implementation ( After options are confirmed)
- with yml, you should make all of them without user input